review: We will definitely be back! Loved it! We did Cell Block Nine as 2 people

room_title: Escape room "Cell Block 9" by Great Escape of Central Texas in Killeen
review: We had an awesome time at our first escape, so much so that we went back to a second room the same night! We tried our Lost and Bank Heist, I would recommend both! Definitely a lot of fun for a family, team, or co-workers to bond and build communication skills. My friend and I went with a group of strangers and it was still a blast.
